This directory contains the following files.

# solution system #
1. min.mdp ; minimization
2. nvt.mdp ; equilibration in NVT
3. npt.mdp ; equilibration in NPT
4. solution_run.mdp and output files (log and xtc) ; production run in NPT

# solvent system #
5. wat.top
6. solvent.gro
(2. nvt.mdp)
(3. npt.mdp)
7. solvent_run.mdp and output files (log and xtc) ; production run in NPT

# solute system #
8. etoh.top
9. etoh.gro
10. solute_min.mdp ; minimization
11. solute_eq.mdp  ; equilibration
12. solute_run.mdp and output file (xtc) ; production run of an isolated system

# sample output of the solvation free energy #
13. slvfe-sample.log
